Q6. Write a program to check if the letter 'e' is present in the word 'Umberalla'. 

Ans:
class Test{
    public static void main(String args[]){
      String str="Umberalla";
      boolean present=false;
      for(int i=0;i<str.length();i++)
      {
        if(str.charAt(i)=='e')
        {
            present=true;
        }
      }
      System.out.print(present);
   }
   }


Q7. Write a program to delete all consonants from the string "Hello,have a good day".

Ans:
class Test{
    public static void main(String args[]){
      String str="Hello,have a good day";
      int n=str.length();
      String str2="";
      for(int i=0;i<n;i++)
      {
        if(str.charAt(i)=='e'||str.charAt(i)=='a'||str.charAt(i)=='i'||str.charAt(i)=='o'||str.charAt(i)=='u'||str.charAt(i)==' ')
        {
            str2=str2+str.charAt(i);
        }
      }
      System.out.print(str2);
   }
